    Get latest data

Get latest data from Washington Post Github Repo

Source: R/latest_data.R
latest_data.Rd

Checks if new data is available from the Washington Post Github repo and returns the most current dataset.

Usage

latest_data()

Value

tibble

Examples

latest_data()
